+        satisfying the large-radius limit
+        \begin{align}
+            V_{\mathrm{soft}}(r) \xrightarrow{r\gg r_c} -\frac{\Lambda_{\mathrm{SST}}}{r}.
+        \end{align}
+        
+        \textbf{[ORTHODOX]}: finite-core regularizations of singular central potentials are standard effective-model tools.\newline
+        \textbf{[DERIVED]}: the SST scale in Eq.~\eqref{eq:lambda_sst} is fixed by canonical constants rather than introduced phenomenologically.\newline
